---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---
<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">A blog about people building for themselves</p>
  <h1>The Age of Personal Software</h1>
  <p class="lede">Personal software is evolving beyond spreadsheets.</p>
  <p class="intro">Personal software used to mean spreadsheets. Now it can mean much more. This blog explores the people using AI to build tools around their own lives.</p>
</section>

<section class="post-listing">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>Posts</h2>
    <p>Stories from people building custom tools around their own workflows.</p>
  </div>

  <ul class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <li class="post-card">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">
          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>Why one builder replaced spreadsheets with an AI-native personal finance tool.</p>
          <span>Read post →</span>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
